Feature: User Valid Login
  As a registered user
  I want to sign in to the application
  So that I can access the user dashboard

  Background:
    Given the login page is displayed

  Scenario: Successful login with valid credentials
    When I enter the valid username 'user'
    And I enter the valid password 'pass'
    And I click the 'Sign In' button
    Then I should be able to observe the user dashboard
;
Feature: Create Odontologist Project
  As a signed-in user
  I want to create a new Odontologist project
  So that users will be able to create surveys

  Background:
    Given I am signed in
    And I can see my dashboard

  Scenario: Create a new Odontologist Project
    When I select to add a new project
    And I set the study title to 'Odontologist project'
    And I set the description to 'This is an Odontologist project'
    And I select to continue
    Then the Odontologist project should appear in the overview dashboard